Defendant Travis Wade Rodgers in court.  Jon D. Seifert appeared for the State of Wisconsin.  Defendant wishes to proceed without counsel.  Waiver of Right to Atty form filed and reviewed.  Court advises defendant of charge/standard penalties.  Defendant pleads no contest.   Court reviews PQWOR with DE.  Court finds defendant's WCR & Plea done K&V, accepts plea and finds defendant guilty.  State recommends 40 hrs. community service, 5 days in PCJ imposed & stayed.  Court reviews community service.  Sentenced to 5 days in the PCJ & stay on completing 40 hrs. C/S; costs $443.00.  TTP granted.  Advised of appeal rights.  Defendant to complete appeal form and TTP app.

Defendant Travis Wade Rodgers in court.  Jon D. Seifert appeared for the State of Wisconsin.  Court confirms defendant received copy of criminal complaint, advises of charges/max. penalties and rights.  Defendant wishes to proceed w/o an atty, files Waiver form with the court.  Court finds defendant WRTA.  Defendant pleads NG.  Defendant requests JT.  Court encourages defendant to contact an attorney, matter adjourned to 11/3.  Status conference scheduled for November 3, 2015 at 02:30 pm.
